caption:
Yang Gang Spring Break 2024.🏝️🏖️🌊
Taking 3 young kids on a trip is always challenging, but always worth it. I wouldn’t call this a vacation, but more like an expedition. I told my kids during dinner one night that I love them so much, I would die for them and then Ryder turned to me and said, “but dad, then who would guide us through life?”🥹 While Ryder misunderstood me, I fully understand how much I mean to him. And that’s all that matters. And it’s what keeps me going. My life hasn’t been about me in a long time, it’s about them. I was supposed to be at LIV Miami this week, but I’ll never miss time with my kids, golf will always be there for me. #DaddyGang #CBC
